{"tid":1515744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[私了撚] 當\"101拘捕令\"變成\"被告非法禁錮\"後...","createTime":"2019-08-29T09:49:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T03:32:31.000Z","uid":119806,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c00767943011a2350dd2bcb0f5b09cf19f42eefc","tid":1515744,"uid":119806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:49:40.000Z","msg":"尋晚美乎捉人嘅義士居然被告非法禁錮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n襲擊者只係告非法襲擊, 而非法禁錮刑期可以判7年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n代價差異太大, 唔值得, 好多巴打建議<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">私了</span></span><br />\n但點做最好呢? 小弟建議大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span></span>做下面嘅野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1, 唔好直接打頭</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打頭會清楚睇到傷勢, 咁記者會影得好清楚<br />\n會嚇驚藍絲唔敢再打人, 為左平衡大家嘅暴力, 千祈唔好做!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>2, 唔好帶漂白水</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 「1比99, 清潔好幫手」, 漂白水係清洗 DNA 證據嘅最好道具<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放入100cc 噴瓶方便攜帶, 又易於使用, 又可以當胡椒噴劑噴狂徒隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都係我唔議嘅, 因為抹左D 犯罪者留低嘅證據, 咁克警就會搜證困難, 有違公義<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>3, 打完人都唔好Call 記者</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n散水後 Call 左記者, 報導左件事, 會嚇親班廢老藍絲, 佢地唔再出嚟打人、斬人, 發洩唔到屈埋屈埋可能會屈到生癌患絕症, 所以為左佢地健康著想, 千祈唔好Call 記者<br />\n<br />\n仲有樣Optional 嘅野都唔太建議, 攞左佢個電話, download 抗爭圖片、videos同抗爭日程, 再喺佢個 WhatsApp、Facebook broadcast 出去<br />\n咁樣制造太多電子垃圾, 大家要環保、愛護地球<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">更加唔好放上Wechat!</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n萬一疑凶番大陸揼骨, 過關捉左困住十幾廿個鐘, 幾咁無辜呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都係愛護香港嘅好手足, 唔想大家出事先有咁嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395aa72af204bf7bed69a0fe8b10d37a8e1d5b20","tid":1515744,"uid":119806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:51:06.000Z","msg":"大家千祈唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339475c075e9616000e5c6415c2cbf87e5ed9233","tid":1515744,"uid":253978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUHazmx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUHazmx.jpg&h=3ccc6422&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6d4a6763720bbe85bc743e68b531625ca3cde21","tid":1515744,"uid":119806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"打人事小 私了事大<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07e3cf4d2f82bd762be22b9d6d8d0859b56307f","tid":1515744,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S7VGF04.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS7VGF04.gif&h=8d2b2993&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=437807b1\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=2a78521d\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http:/