67b4f1e0f32d607254fa119915e42c7d0","tid":1515744,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"101只係一個都市傳說"},{"pid":"915058500404d1d9a98cc0dd8e3a0fcec6346ddc","tid":1515744,"uid":19743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n借個位黎<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1487629/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人撐香港隊<br />\n入場向世界表達訴求<br />\n賽前有奏鄰國國歌儀式，大家識做!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eC7JUxG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeC7JUxG.png&h=4352d932&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3BKDZn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3BKDZn.png&h=fd2e6806&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qQHFcjE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqQHFcjE.jpg&h=6cb0627d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地仲可以用香港隊名義踢國際賽係因為我地同中國足協係完全分開運作<br />\n有自己既地方聯賽<br />\n如果可以既話<br />\n希望咁多位可以多多支持香港超級足球聯賽<br />\n因為香港足總成日話港超無出路<br />\n要返中國聯賽/大灣區聯賽"},{"pid":"71856e10322ecf6ad3de1dcd0c0e954480aa5a5f","tid":1515744,"uid":188337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"981ac728c825548ed75344d8b5ea1504129aa09a","tid":1515744,"uid":166405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:18:43.000Z","msg":"報警撚害死人"},{"pid":"f668003e362a44e77719d00bc06f003458c68c98","tid":1515744,"uid":119806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:19:47.000Z","msg":"鐵通打人罰兩k 不如掩左佢條J<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629beda02fa7deb6a299e93f34096b0208b09621","t